Tadka of ghee

Put toor dal into a cooker and wait for three whistles.
Put in ghee and then put in mustard seeds and curry leaves.
Put in carrots and let it fry. Then put beans in. When carrots are frying, add 1 spoon chili powder, 1/5 spoon turmeric, 2 spoon sambar
podi, 1 spoon of coriander powder, and 3-4 spoon of salt accordingly. Add tomatoes and chillies in blender and pour over tadka with water.
Then add to dhal, and add one spoon of puli paste. 

(for 1 - 1.5 cup dhal). Serve 3 to 4 times. 
